        "subject": "LU-7312 test: With set -e exit status in sanity-hsm was not valid",
        "message": "LU-7312 test: With set -e exit status in sanity-hsm was not valid\n\nThe exit status which was obtained using $? in copytool_cleanup\nfunction wasn't returning a valid value thereby leading to\nimproper verification and thus exiting from the script. The fix\ndoes the appropriate error handling caused due to set -e and\ndoes the proper cleanup at the end.\n\nSeagate-Bug-id: MRP-2578\nSigned-off-by: Bhagyesh Dudhediya <bhagyesh.dudhediya@seagate.com>\nChange-Id: I16bc00ec4ebb18ac25237da9667a8bbea6566c5b\n"
      },
